initial release of F.G is out, perhaps you guys could spend the time 
you might need researching and experimenting with the mathematics 
that I would imagine are required to auto generate triangulated 
landscapes.  Perhaps you could start out by using U.S.G.S data in 
your computations, similar to Scbuild's road, river, lake, etc 
compiling routines?

I think it might be helphul to contact Hans Meier and let him know 
